ObjectCombos.Name: [!] Box
ObjectCombos.BP1_DESCRIPTION: The star number when 'Content' is equal to 8 (Star)
ObjectCombos.BP2_DESCRIPTION:
The item inside the [!] Box.
0 = Wing Cap, 1 = Metal Cap
2 = Vanish Cap, 3 = Koopa Shell
4 = One Coin, 5 = Five Coins
6 = Ten Coins, 7 = 1-Up Mushroom
8 = Star, 9 = 1-Up (Running away)
10 = Star 1, 11 = Star 2
12 = Star 3, 13 = Star 4
14 = Star 5, 15 = Empty

ObjectCombos.Name: Coin Formation
ObjectCombos.BP2_DESCRIPTION:
0: Five coins horizontal
2: Coin ring horizontal
4: Coin arrow
16: Five coins horizontal flying
17: Five coins vertical
18: Coin ring horizontal flying
19: Coin ring vertical

ObjectCombos.Name: Star for Red Coins (Hidden, Bowser Levels)
Switchblock [MOP2]
ObjectCombos.BP1_DESCRIPTION:
0 to start red
2 to start blue

ObjectCombos.Name: Checkpoint Flag [MOP3]
ObjectCombos.BP2_DESCRIPTION:
0 for regular flag
1 for reset flag
